ichelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/memory-db-file-topology.md\",\n          \"title\": \"MEMORY — Spec-Kit DB File Topology (index vs vectors are SEPARATE files)\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: MEMORY — Spec-Kit DB File Topology (index vs vectors are SEPARATE files) | Prioritize when: task context aligns with \\\"MEMORY — Spec-Kit DB File Topology (index vs vectors are SEPARATE files)\\\"\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": 9373,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/main-branch-direct-push.md\",\n          \"title\": \"Main Branch — Owner's AIs Push Directly\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: rule applies — Do NOT default to a feature-branch + PR flow, do NOT re-ask whether to use a PR, and do NOT flag the bypass or the unsi… | Prioritize when: only (the tree often has concurrent parallel-session work + daemon metadata churn — NEVER `git add -A` blindly; use exp…\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": 9372,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/gate-tool-routing.md\",\n          \"title\": \"TOOL ROUTING - Search & Retrieval Decision Tree\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: TOOL ROUTING - Search & Retrieval Decision Tree | Prioritize when: task context aligns with \\\"TOOL ROUTING - Search & Retrieval Decision Tree\\\"\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"triggered\": [\n        {\n          \"memory_id\": 6891,\n          \"spec_folder\": \"system-spec-kit/z_archive/001-fix-command-dispatch/z_archive/049-system-analysis-bugs\",\n          \"title\": \"System-Spec-Kit Bug [system-spec-kit/z_archive/001-fix-command-dispatch/z_archive/049-system-analysis-bugs/spec]\",\n          \"matched_phrases\": [\n            \"system\",\n            \"spec\",\n            \"kit\",\n            \"analysis\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"memory_id\": 6831,\n          \"spec_folder\": \"system-spec-kit/z_archive/001-fix-command-dispatch/z_archive/042-post-merge-refinement-5\",\n          \"title\": \"Spec Kit [system-spec-kit/z_archive/001-fix-command-dispatch/z_archive/042-post-merge-refinement-5/decision-record]\",\n          \"matched_phrases\": [\n            \"spec\",\n            \"kit\",\n            \"memory\",\n            \"system\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"memory_id\": 6742,\n          \"spec_folder\": \"system-spec-kit/z_archive/001-fix-command-dispatch/z_archive/027-memory-plugin-and-refinement/001-memory-repo-analysis\",\n          \"title\": \"...spec-kit/z_archive/001-fix-command-dispatch/z_archive/027-memory-plugin-and-refinement/001-memory-repo-analysis/spec]\",\n          \"matched_phrases\": [\n            \"memory\",\n            \"system\",\n            \"analysis\",\n            \"spec\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"memory_id\": 8514,\n          \"spec_folder\": \"system-spec-kit/z_archive/023-hybrid-rag-fusion-refinement\",\n          \"title\": \"Deep Research: Spec Kit Memory Feature Audit & Quality [system-spec-kit/023-hybrid-rag-fusion-refinement/research]\",\n          \"matched_phrases\": [\n            \"research\",\n            \"spec\",\n            \"kit\",\n            \"memory\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"memory_id\": 7589,\n          \"spec_folder\": \"system-spec-kit/z_archive/022-hybrid-rag-fusion/005-architecture-audit\",\n          \"title\": \"System-Spec-Kit Architecture Audit v2 [system-spec-kit/022-hybrid-rag-fusion/005-architecture-audit/research]\",\n          \"matched_phrases\": [\n            \"system\",\n            \"spec\",\n            \"kit\",\n            \"research\"\n          ]\n        }\n      ],\n      \"surfaced_at\": \"2026-06-06T06:41:21.795Z\",\n      \"latencyMs\": 3075\n    },\n    \"tokenBudget\": 3500\n  }\n}","metadata":{"truncated":false},"title":"","time":{"start":1780728073942,"end":1780728082814}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_09749648b7212dab016a23c1050d94819188eebd4bbf901a3b"}},"id":"prt_e9ba9fcfd001bfoFUyeU96gHIb","sessionID":"ses_164567595ffekYKAW3lqY5njlC","messageID":"msg_e9ba98fc6001szYT20G7Q31YHT"}}
